title: (Mon Full) The Worst Thing from Our Vacations: Amy Returns with a Cough + Abby’s Top 5 Best and Sketchy Moments from Her Solo Vacation + Caller Sarah Needs Advice on Living With Someone for the First Time
itunes:title: (Mon Full) The Worst Thing from Our Vacations: Amy Returns with a Cough + Abby’s Top 5 Best and Sketchy Moments from Her Solo Vacation + Caller Sarah Needs Advice on Living With Someone for the First Time
description:
We each share the worst things that happened to us on our vacation that includes Amy getting sick on the final day of break. Abby shares the high and low lights from her solo vacation that Eddie and Scuba Steve convinced her to go on. Listener Sarah calls in who is about to move in with her boyfriend. She asks us for advice on living with someone for the first time.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
